gomodel:SYNGO_4697  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 6: Bcl-xL (BCL2L1) and Drp1 co-localize with synaptophysin on synaptic vesicles as shown by immunogold EM of cultured hippocampal neurons. Note that Bcl-xL and Drp1 were also found to be localized to mitochondria.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Primary rat hippocampal neurons were prepared as described previously...\"\n\nantibody: Rabbit mAb anti-Bcl-xL antibody 54H6 (#2764, Cell Signaling Technology, 1:1,000)\n\ntarget gene BCL2L1 confirmed from cell signaling website, which links to UniProt ID: Q07817 and Entrez-Gene Id: 598" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
